#. Id: 95814-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Robotics shop black desert
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: MET_TARGET_BEFORE=0, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IS_SAME_RACE_AS_ME=0, Tag: -1
#: 95814-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "A human?... It's not everyday I get a human customer... but, sure, I've got plenty of parts that should fit you fine indeed... Did you travel all the way here just for my expertise?... Gosh... I'm flattered... I don't blame you though, human, flesh is good for nothing but rotting... Where was I going with this?"
msgstr "一個人？...我不是每天都會得到一個人類客戶......但是，當然，我有很多適合你的部分......你為了我的專長而一直在這裡旅行嗎？天啊......我很受寵若驚......但是我不怪你，人類，肉體只有腐爛才有好處......我在這裡走的是什麼？"

#. Id: 95813-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (95814-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Robotics shop black desert
#: 95813-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "... Right that was it, guess you're looking to buy some parts? Or maybe you're looking for some repairs? I can fix anything, trust me, years of experience. Everybody thinks they're a robotics expert these days I bet, but they've got nothing on the robotics capital of the land, believe you me... You were right to pilgrimage hundreds of miles just to seek me out, I really am good at this stuff... Where was I going with this?"
msgstr "......就是這樣，你猜你想買一些零件嗎？或者也許你正在尋找一些維修？我可以解決任何問題，相信我，多年的經驗。我敢打賭，現在每個人都認為他們是機器人技術專家，但是他們對這片土地上的機器人資本一無所知，相信你我......你是朝向數百英里朝聖的對象，只是為了尋找我，我真的是擅長這個東西......我在哪裡這個？"

#. Id: 95816-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (95813-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Robotics shop black desert
#: 95816-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I need repair."
msgstr "我需要修理。"

#. Id: 95819-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (95816-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Robotics shop black desert
#: 95819-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "That will be 1000 Cats..."
msgstr "這將是1000貓......"

#. Id: 95820-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (95819-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Robotics shop black desert
#: 95820-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Lie on the repair bed when you're ready."
msgstr "準備好時躺在修理床上。"

#. Id: 97582-__March 18.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (95816-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Robotics shop black desert
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: HAS_ROBOT_LIMBS=0, Tag: -1
#: 97582-__March?18.mod:0
msgid "But... You have nothing to repair."
msgstr "但是......你無需修理。"

#. Id: 97584-__March 18.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (95816-Dialogue.mod)
